First Option Dashboard

A secure, multilingual banking dashboard built for 1st Option LLC and Asset Control+. This modular platform empowers users with real-time investor tools, branded receipt generation, wallet onboarding flows, and international compliance alerts.

Key Features:
- 💼 Account summary and transaction history  
- 📊 Investor dashboard with live charts and profit/loss tracking  
- 🧾 Bilingual, legally compliant receipt generator with QR codes  
- 🌍 Multilingual routing and international onboarding flows  
- 🔐 JWT-secured backend with modular API architecture  
- 🛡 Compliance-ready identity fields and legal disclaimers  

Designed for scalability, trust, and global reach—this repo blends fintech precision with user-first design.
